    public static enum Resource.IsolationLevel
extends java.lang.Enum<Resource.IsolationLevel>
    The isolation level for the data returned by the resource.
    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      READ_COMMITTED
      Indicates that all methods should return a consistent view of the resource data and metadata.
      READ_UNCOMMITTED
      Indicates that the various methods may not return a consistent view of the resource data or metadata.
